{"ID":"20260609132126-7tw32ac","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609132126-7tw32ac","title":"2021年全国乙卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609132143-f72vypw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132143-f72vypw","updated":"20260609132143"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有人说，互联网虽然实现了我们的一个古老的梦想，把远在天涯的人变得"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，但与此同时也可能恰好相反，把身边的人变得如在天涯，因而引发了一种普遍的担心：当我们越来越习惯于线上的虚拟世界时，我们是否会最终失去与现实世界的联系。对线上虚拟世界的担心，并非"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。正如有研究者指出的那样，互联网已经深入到我们生活中的方方面面，过度沉迷有可能让一些人“越来越拥抱技术、越来越忽略彼此”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132143-4vr81yv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132143-4vr81yv","updated":"20260609132143"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实际上，线上与线下之间的界限也不是那么"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。研究发现，互联网中的社交关系大多是通过“上传”线下的好友形成的，是现实社交的延续。从空间角度来讲，互联网有助于我们维系远距离的线下关系；从时间角度来看，媒介化创造了一种广泛的双向即时互动。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"空间和时间由于不断压缩，大大增强了互动性，社会交往效率有助于得到显著提高。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（       ）。“虚拟”与“现实”早已是你中有我，我中有你。现实世界为虚拟生活"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"地提供养料，虚拟生活又能激发和充实现实世界的活力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132126-kutl9h3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609132126-kutl9h3","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-x1wten7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-x1wten7","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．依次填入文中横线上的词语，全都恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-cdj980y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-cdj980y","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．近在咫尺        杞人忧天        泾渭分明      源源不断"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-f0bq4y9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-f0bq4y9","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．触手可及        空穴来风        泾渭分明      取之不尽"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-ibuwu64","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-ibuwu64","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．近在咫尺        空穴来风        非此即彼      源源不断"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-p0wrag8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-p0wrag8","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．触手可及        杞人忧天        非此即彼      取之不尽"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-964z5z1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-964z5z1","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．下列填入文中括号内的语句，衔接最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-eg8uccs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-eg8uccs","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．社会交往是如此，我们工作和生活的其他方面也是如此"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-u0nz4cm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-u0nz4cm","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．不但社会交往如此，而且我们工作和生活的其他方面也是如此"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-ebos21a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-ebos21a","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．我们工作和生活的其他方面，和社会交往也是一样的"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-jyzjg0r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-jyzjg0r","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．我们工作和生活的其他方面也是这样，除了社会交往"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-8a2h2d1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-8a2h2d1","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．文中画波浪线的句子有语病，下列修改最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-88ohehv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-88ohehv","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．由于空间和时间不断压缩，大大增强了互动性，有助于社会交往效率显著提高。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-aaemig5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-aaemig5","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．由于空间和时间不断压缩，大大增强了互动性，社会交往效率得到显著提高。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-gotq1u3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-gotq1u3","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．空间和时间由于不断压缩，互动性大大增强，社会交往效率得到显著提高。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132154-0rbkw03","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132154-0rbkw03","updated":"20260609132154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．空间和时间由于不断压缩，互动性大大增强，有助于社会交往效率显著提高。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132126-skt537v","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609132126-skt537v","updated":"20260609132201"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609132126-lt3iy91","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132126-lt3iy91","updated":"20260609132201"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．A    18．A    19．B"}]},{"ID":"20260609132126-1hhuhav","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609132126-1hhuhav","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-miqm06r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-miqm06r","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．本题考查学生正确使用成语的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-ekyrmtj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-ekyrmtj","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"近在咫尺：形容距离很近。触手可及：指近在手边，一伸手就可以接触到。语境是形容距离极近，但并非实指。再根据语境中的“远在天涯”可推知，应选“近在咫尺”；"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-c6t4fnp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-c6t4fnp","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杞人忧天：总是去忧虑那些不切实际的事物。比喻毫无必要的忧虑和担心。空穴来风：有了空穴才有风进来。比喻流言、消息的传播不是完全没有原因的。现多用来指消息和传闻毫无根据。语境说的是对线上虚拟世界的担心并非没有必要，应选“杞人忧天”；"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-pjmvvyq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-pjmvvyq","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泾渭分明：泾河水清，渭河水浑，泾河的水流入渭河时，清浊不混。比喻界限清楚或是非分明。非此即彼：意思是不是这一个，就是那一个。语境是说现在线上线下的界限越来越模糊，再联系后文“‘虚拟’与‘现实’早已是你中有我，我中有你”，可知应选“泾渭分明”；"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-au2xtlh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-au2xtlh","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"源源不断：形容接连不断、连绵不绝。多用于事物，而少用于人。取之不尽：形容物质或精神的原料极其丰富。语境中有“提供养料”，应选“源源不断”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-c8e207d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-c8e207d","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-dkd7yf3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-dkd7yf3","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．本题考查学生语言表达连贯的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-a067j45","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-a067j45","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"括号前面说的是“互联网中的社交关系”，也就是“社会交往”，因此应以“社会交往”开头与前面衔接；括号后面说“‘虚拟’与‘现实’早已是你中有我，我中有你”，这是说现实生活中也是这样；而“社会交往”与“现实生活”的关系是并列关系。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-8mdakwj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-8mdakwj","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.将二者关系定位为递进关系，不正确；"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-01e9fks","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-01e9fks","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.应先说“社会交往”，再说“工作和生活”；"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-hnhyegt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-hnhyegt","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.“除了社会交往”说法错误，且应先说“社会交往”，再说“工作和生活”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-r25ww7l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-r25ww7l","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-lomawn3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-lomawn3","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．本题考查学生辨析并修改病句的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-4bj3n5a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-4bj3n5a","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"原句语病有：“空间和时间由于不断压缩，大大增强了互动性”语序不当，“空间和时间不断压缩”是后面“互动性增强”的原因，“由于”应该放在前面，应改为“由于空间和时间不断压缩，大大增强了互动性”；"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-gfgz76p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-gfgz76p","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“社会交往效率有助于得到显著提高”句式杂糅，要么说“……得到显著提高”，要么说“有助于……提高”，可改为“社会交往效率得到显著提高”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-rezzv5g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-rezzv5g","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"综合分析可知，只有B项修改正确。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132214-c8inn6w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132214-c8inn6w","updated":"20260609132214"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]}]}